msgid "4. Hatthārohasutta"
msgstr "4. An Elephant Warrior"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.310"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho hatthāroho gāmaṇi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe …"
msgstr "Then an elephant warrior chief went up to the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn42.4:1.2"
msgid "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatanti."
msgstr ""
"“From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
